Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.98,0:08:17.89,Utama,Komura,0,0,0,,Ja-Jangan paksain diri.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.29,0:08:28.10,Utama,Mie,0,0,0,,Enggak bisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.10,0:08:29.34,Utama,Mie,0,0,0,,Malah nangis!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.34,0:08:30.40,Utama,Komura,0,0,0,,Mi-Mie-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.52,0:08:33.25,Utama,Komura,0,0,0,,Mending tidak usah dipakai.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.25,0:08:34.40,Utama,Komura,0,0,0,,Jangan paksakan dirimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.40,0:08:35.68,Utama,Mie,0,0,0,,Tapi ....
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.68,0:08:37.88,Utama,Komura,0,0,0,,A-Aku akan melindungimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.59,0:08:43.22,Utama,Komura,0,0,0,,Aku akan melindungimu walau kau tidak memakai kacamata atau lensa kontak!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.22,0:08:44.21,Utama,Komura,0,0,0,,Jangan khawatir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.03,0:08:49.24,Utama,Mie,0,0,0,,Menggebu-gebu banget, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.44,0:08:57.83,Utama,Mie,0,0,0,,Terima kasih, Komura-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.22,0:09:00.86,Miring,Mie,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}Terima kasih, Komura-kun
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.07,0:09:03.48,Miring,Mie,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}Terima kasih, Komura-kun
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.66,0:09:06.01,Miring,Mie,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}Terima kasih, Komura-kun
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.17,0:09:08.48,Miring,Mie,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}Terima kasih, Komura-kun
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.15,0:09:11.44,Utama,Komura,0,0,0,,Pa-Pakailah ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.44,0:09:12.52,Utama,Mie,0,0,0,,Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.99,0:09:15.82,Miring,Komura,0,0,0,,Akupun ingin melindunginya hingga akhir hayatku.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.90,0:09:33.01,Miring,Komura,0,0,0,,Padahal pakai kacamata, tapi tatapannya sinis?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.23,0:09:35.92,Miring,Komura,0,0,0,,A-Apa yang terjadi?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.92,0:09:37.76,Miring,Komura,0,0,0,,Misteri misterius.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.49,0:09:41.29,Miring,Komura,0,0,0,,Apakah ini tantangan untukku?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.78,0:09:45.77,Miring,Komura,0,0,0,,Apa aku yang satu-satunya \Nharus memecahkan misteri Mie-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.10,0:09:47.73,Utama,Mie,0,0,0,,Pagi, Komura-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.14,0:09:49.79,Utama,Komura,0,0,0,,Pa-Pagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.79,0:09:53.91,Utama,Komura,0,0,0,,Anu, kenapa kau menyipitkan matamu\N walau sudah pakai kacamata?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.44,0:09:58.80,Utama,Mie,0,0,0,,Di luar panas banget, kacamataku jadi mengembun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.80,0:10:01.16,Miring,Komura,0,0,0,,Bi-Bisa seperti itu juga?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.43,0:10:06.16,Utama,Mie,0,0,0,,Padahal aku sudah gerah banget, \N jangan ngehalangin kacamataku juga, dong.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.72,0:10:09.67,Utama,Mie,0,0,0,,Tapi sekarang aman karena di dalam kelas, sih.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.67,0:10:12.52,Miring,Komura,0,0,0,,Ucapannya selalu tak bisa kusangkal,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.52,0:10:15.33,Miring,Komura,0,0,0,,tapi rupanya dia punya banyak masalah, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.55,0:10:18.48,Atas,Tokita,0,0,0,,Pagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.55,0:10:19.68,Miring,Komura,0,0,0,,Kacamata Tokita-kun juga mengembun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.59,0:10:19.68,Atas,Classmates,0,0,0,,Pagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.60,0:10:22.75,Miring,Komura,0,0,0,,Kacanya terlihat burik.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.75,0:10:24.02,Utama,Mie,0,0,0,,Komura-kun ....
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.68,0:10:32.90,Utama,Mie,0,0,0,,Ada orang asing di kelas!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.72,0:10:36.06,Utama,Mie,0,0,0,,Apa sebaiknya kupanggil guru?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.06,0:10:37.34,Utama,Komura,0,0,0,,Di-Dia Tokita-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.34,0:10:38.65,Utama,Komura,0,0,0,,Dia tema sekelas!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.65,0:10:39.45,Utama,Mie,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.25,0:10:44.78,Utama,Mie,0,0,0,,Aku enggak kenal karena matanya tertutup.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.78,0:10:45.41,Miring,Komura,0,0,0,,Ya ampun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.99,0:10:50.36,Utama,Mie,0,0,0,,Apa aku juga enggak dikenalin orang lain, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.36,0:10:51.42,Utama,Komura,0,0,0,,Tidak .....
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.17,0:10:54.35,Utama,Komura,0,0,0,,Mungkin tidak apa-apa, kok.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.03,0:10:56.42,Utama,Mie,0,0,0,,Yah, sudahlah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.27,0:11:00.18,Utama,Mie,0,0,0,,Asal kamu mengenaliku, enggak masalah, Komura-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.51,0:11:03.36,Miring,Mie,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}Asal kamu mengenaliku, enggak masalah, Komura-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.72,0:11:06.60,Miring,Mie,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}Asal kamu mengenaliku, enggak masalah, Komura-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.95,0:11:09.81,Miring,Mie,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}Asal kamu mengenaliku, enggak masalah, Komura-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.08,0:11:13.00,Miring,Mie,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}Asal kamu mengenaliku, enggak masalah, Komura-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.44,0:11:19.58,Utama,Mie,0,0,0,,Oh ya, pindah ruangan, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.80,0:11:22.15,Miring,Komura,0,0,0,,Tu-Tunggu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.15,0:11:24.34,Miring,Komura,0,0,0,,Aku masih terpesona!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.34,0:11:26.62,Miring,Komura,0,0,0,,Jangan pergi dulu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.02,0:11:34.58,Utama,Mie,0,0,0,,Komura-kun, bisa kasih tahu akun LIME-mu?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.76,0:11:40.16,Utama,Komura,0,0,0,,Si-Siap kukasih tahu berkali-kali.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.16,0:11:41.84,Utama,Mie,0,0,0,,Satu kali cukup, kok.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.12,0:11:45.48,Utama,Komura,0,0,0,,Ta-Tapi kenapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.48,0:11:49.16,Utama,Mie,0,0,0,,Aku sering lupa bawa kacamata, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.62,0:11:55.77,Utama,Mie,0,0,0,,Untuk jaga-jaga keadaan terdesak,\N aku ingin minta bantuanmu, Komura-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.77,0:11:57.98,Miring,Komura,0,0,0,,Dia masih yakin bakal sering lupa, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.78,0:12:01.07,Utama,Komura,0,0,0,,A-Apa kau yakin denganku?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.07,0:12:02.74,Utama,Komura,0,0,0,,Bukankah lebih baik menghubungi keluargamu?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.74,0:12:04.02,Utama,Mie,0,0,0,,Aku enggak sanggup bilang.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.02,0:12:07.12,Utama,Mie,0,0,0,,Pasti malu-maluin lupa bawa kacamata, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.12,0:12:09.09,Miring,Komura,0,0,0,,Dia merasa malu, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.09,0:12:09.96,Utama,Mie,0,0,0,,Tapi ....
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.09,0:12:16.50,Utama,Mie,0,0,0,,Tapi aku enggak masalah malu di depanmu, Komura-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.10,0:12:20.51,Miring,Mie,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}Enggak masalah malu di depanmu, Komura-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.89,0:12:23.17,Miring,Mie,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}Enggak masalah malu di depanmu, Komura-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.28,0:12:25.51,Miring,Mie,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}Enggak masalah malu di depanmu, Komura-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.53,0:12:31.02,Utama,Mie,0,0,0,,Lagian aku sudah sering lupa pakai kacamata \Ndan memalukan di depanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.60,0:12:33.46,Utama,Mie,0,0,0,,Maaf malah bergantung padamu, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.19,0:12:38.30,Utama,Mie,0,0,0,,Komura-kun?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:41.94,0:12:43.90,Utama,Mie,0,0,0,,Apa kamu senggang, Komura-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.90,0:12:47.98,Utama,Mie,0,0,0,,Kalau senggang, bisa datang ke Stasiun Kichijoji?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.72,0:12:52.40,Miring,Komura,0,0,0,,Komura Kaede, 13 tahun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.40,0:12:53.27,Miring,Komura,0,0,0,,Musim panas tiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.79,0:12:56.66,Miring,Komura,0,0,0,,Walau belum lama ini aku bertukar \Nkontak LIME dengen Mie-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.63,0:13:00.34,Miring,Komura,0,0,0,,tapi tak kusangka dia mengajakku pergi sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.34,0:13:03.30,Miring,Komura,0,0,0,,Saking kagetnya aku jatuh dari kasur.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.56,0:13:09.22,Utama,Mob Woman A,0,0,0,,Aku datang.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.22,0:13:09.71,Utama,Mob Man B,0,0,0,,Iya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.71,0:13:10.31,Utama,Mob Woman A,0,0,0,,Ayo pergi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.52,0:13:11.40,Miring,Komura,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.22,0:13:16.96,Miring,Komura,0,0,0,,Sekitar sini, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.54,0:13:23.22,Miring,Komura,0,0,0,,Mi-Mie-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.22,0:13:24.75,Miring,Komura,0,0,0,,Dia lupa kacamatanya!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.42,0:13:27.32,Utama,Mie,0,0,0,,Komura-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.32,0:13:28.69,Utama,Mie,0,0,0,,Maaf telah memanggilmu ke sini, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.69,0:13:30.16,Utama,Komura,0,0,0,,Tidak apa-apa ....
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.16,0:13:31.91,Utama,Komura,0,0,0,,Kau lupa bawa kacamata?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.91,0:13:34.45,Utama,Mie,0,0,0,,Aku ketiduran di dalam kereta.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.25,0:13:39.15,Utama,Mie,0,0,0,,Akupun turun dengan buru-buru ....
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.12,0:13:47.29,Utama,Mie,0,0,0,,Tapi rasanya ada yang hilang dariku.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.68,0:13:52.80,Utama,Komura,0,0,0,,Kayaknya kau tidak cocok pakai kacamata, deh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.80,0:13:56.96,Utama,Mie,0,0,0,,Tapi ada tempat yang harus hamba kunjungi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.96,0:13:58.60,Utama,Mie,0,0,0,,Hamba ingin minta tolong antarkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.42,0:14:02.46,Miring,Komura,0,0,0,,Terkadang nomongnya mirip samurai, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.97,0:14:05.18,Miring,Komura,0,0,0,,Eh? Tapi bukankah ....
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.18,0:14:07.71,Miring,Komura,0,0,0,,Pergi berdua ke kota pada akhir pekan ....
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.64,0:14:11.87,Miring,Komura,0,0,0,,Ini namanya ken--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.63,0:14:14.62,Miring,Komura,0,0,0,,Ini namanya ken ....
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.28,0:14:19.12,Miring,Komura,0,0,0,,Tidak, walau aku tahu ini bukan,\Ntapi aku senang!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.12,0:14:21.63,Miring,Komura,0,0,0,,Mungkin aku bakal mati ketiban bahagia!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.00,0:14:24.80,Utama,Komura,0,0,0,,Ka-Kalau tidak keberatan denganku,\Naku siap mengantarmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.80,0:14:28.75,Utama,Mie,0,0,0,,Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.49,0:14:30.89,Utama,Mie,0,0,0,,Gandeng aku, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.32,0:14:33.36,Miring,Mie,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.92,0:14:35.34,Miring,Mie,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}Gandeng aku, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.73,0:14:39.83,Utama,Mie,0,0,0,,Tempat yang ingin aku kunjungi itu ....
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.88,0:14:44.06,Utama,Mie,0,0,0,,Komura-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.06,0:14:47.86,Miring,Komura,0,0,0,,Mungkin aku bakal mati antara besok atau lusa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.48,0:14:53.87,Miring,Komura,0,0,0,,Tidak, tidak ....
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.09,0:14:55.98,Miring,Komura,0,0,0,,Apa boleh kugandeng terus?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.71,0:14:58.41,Miring,Komura,0,0,0,,Apa boleh kugandeng terus?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.41,0:14:59.65,Miring,Komura,0,0,0,,Beneran?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.37,0:15:05.80,Utama,Mie,0,0,0,,Etto ... apa ini tempat yang kau maksud?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.78,0:15:09.31,Utama,Shop,0,0,0,,Silakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.96,0:15:11.96,Utama,Mie,0,0,0,,Kue edisi terbatas di hari Sabtu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.96,0:15:15.68,Utama,Mie,0,0,0,,Aku ngidam-ngidam setengah mati.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.56,0:15:18.21,Miring,Komura,0,0,0,,Dia suka kue, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.63,0:15:19.68,Miring,Komura,0,0,0,,Imutnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.68,0:15:33.01,Miring,Komura,0,0,0,,Dia tidak bisa memotong kuenya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.01,0:15:34.31,Utama,Mie,0,0,0,,Susah dimakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.30,0:15:39.32,Utama,Komura,0,0,0,,Etto ....
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.32,0:15:40.12,Utama,Komura,0,0,0,,Bagaimana ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.60,0:15:42.62,Utama,Komura,0,0,0,,Ah, biar kusuapi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.88,0:15:47.35,Utama,Komura,0,0,0,,Ma-Maaf!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.35,0:15:48.63,Utama,Komura,0,0,0,,Bukan apa-apa! Salah ngomong!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.63,0:15:49.50,Utama,Komura,0,0,0,,Lupakan saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.50,0:15:50.88,Utama,Komura,0,0,0,,Aku minta maaf--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.22,0:15:56.89,Miring,Komura,0,0,0,,Bukankah ini hal terlarang?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.53,0:16:02.46,Miring,Komura,0,0,0,,Harusnya aku menemui Ayahnya \Ndan meminta restunya dulu, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.40,0:16:04.87,Miring,Komura,0,0,0,,Tapi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.27,0:16:09.95,Miring,Komura,0,0,0,,Yang paling terlarang adalah kelanjutannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.58,0:16:18.44,Utama,Mie,0,0,0,,Enak.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.44,0:16:19.26,Utama,Mie,0,0,0,,Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.26,0:16:21.02,Utama,Komura,0,0,0,,{\i1}12 kali kunyah sebelum dia menelannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.62,0:16:25.17,Miring,Komura,0,0,0,,Sekalian aku membayangkan \Nmeminta maaf kepada Ayahnya 12 kali.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.24,0:16:31.42,Utama,Komura,0,0,0,,Ah, selanjutnya kau ingin ke sini, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.14,0:16:33.33,Utama,Komura,0,0,0,,Toko kacamata?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.33,0:16:34.19,Utama,Mie,0,0,0,,Iya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.19,0:16:35.97,Utama,Mie,0,0,0,,Lensaku sudah enggak cocok lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.97,0:16:38.68,frames,Mie,0,0,0,,{\frz357.6\pos(120.094,320)}Menerima Pesanan
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.64,0:16:38.68,Utama,Mie,0,0,0,,Makanya aku pesan yang baru.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.55,0:16:41.98,Utama,Mie,0,0,0,,Dan hari ini sudah bisa diambil.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.54,0:16:44.53,Miring,Komura,0,0,0,,Ini tujuan utamanya, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.68,0:16:54.36,Utama,Mie,0,0,0,,Semua terlihat jelas.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.36,0:16:56.22,Miring,Komura,0,0,0,,Ucapannya kayak dewi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.53,0:17:01.79,Miring,Komura,0,0,0,,Berarti tugasku sudah tuntas.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.21,0:17:05.69,Miring,Komura,0,0,0,,Aku tahu tidak mungkin aku tidak mencuci tangan,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.45,0:17:11.38,Miring,Komura,0,0,0,,tapi aku ingin mengelap dan mengawetkannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.07,0:17:16.42,Asa,Text; Narration,0,0,0,,Cowok kalau sudah mendem kasmaran suka jorok.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.53,0:17:20.17,Utama,Komura,0,0,0,,Baiklah ....
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.42,0:17:23.03,Utama,Komura,0,0,0,,Terima kasih untuk hari ini, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.43,0:17:24.38,Utama,Mie,0,0,0,,Aku juga terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.38,0:17:25.52,Utama,Komura,0,0,0,,Dah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.75,0:17:34.03,Utama,Mie,0,0,0,,Kamu buru-buru?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.90,0:17:36.70,Utama,Komura,0,0,0,,Ti-Tidak.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.70,0:17:39.03,Utama,Komura,0,0,0,,Aku malah senggang, sih.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.54,0:17:42.73,Utama,Mie,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu, temani aku lebih lama lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.00,0:17:47.43,Utama,Mie,0,0,0,,Mumpung aku sudah bisa melihatmu sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.69,0:17:59.60,Utama,Mie,0,0,0,,Kenapa kamu memalingkan wajah?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.60,0:18:00.92,Utama,Komura,0,0,0,,Eh? Anu ....
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.92,0:18:02.60,Utama,Komura,0,0,0,,E-Entahlah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.85,0:18:05.98,Utama,Mie,0,0,0,,Kira-kira dapat enggak, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.98,0:18:07.18,Utama,Komura,0,0,0,,Coba lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.45,0:18:12.22,Utama,Mie,0,0,0,,Enak.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.22,0:18:13.64,Utama,Komura,0,0,0,,Baru kali ini aku meminumnya,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.64,0:18:14.61,Utama,Komura,0,0,0,,tapi enak, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.31,0:18:18.96,Utama,Mie,0,0,0,,Terima kasih untuk hari ini, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.96,0:18:20.95,Utama,Mie,0,0,0,,Aku senang banget.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.18,0:18:22.90,Utama,Komura,0,0,0,,Ti-Tidak, harusnya aku yang senang.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.90,0:18:25.85,Utama,Komura,0,0,0,,Kesenanganku tak bisa diungkapkan\N oleh semua kata di dunia.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.85,0:18:27.65,Utama,Mie,0,0,0,,Aku senang mendengarnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.65,0:18:29.78,Utama,Mie,0,0,0,,Dah, sampai jumpa di sekolah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.69,0:18:47.75,Miring,Komura,0,0,0,,Hari ini bagaikan mimpi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.00,0:18:52.88,Miring,Komura,0,0,0,,Tapi saat kucubit pipiku rasanya sakit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.88,0:18:54.36,Miring,Komura,0,0,0,,Ini bukan mimpi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.86,0:18:59.12,Miring,Komura,0,0,0,,Mau berulang kali kucubit paha atau kupingku ....
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.12,0:19:00.70,Miring,Komura,0,0,0,,Aku merasa sakit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.75,0:19:03.66,Miring,Komura,0,0,0,,Ini sungguh bukan mimpi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.12,0:19:14.32,Miring,Mie,0,0,0,,Komura-kun orang yang baik, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.32,0:19:18.27,Miring,Mie,0,0,0,,Padahal aku mengundangnya dengan paksa, \Ntapi dia enggak pernah ngeluh.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.93,0:19:22.02,Miring,Mie,0,0,0,,Terima kasihku enggak akan pernah cukup.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.62,0:19:25.73,Kilas,Komura,0,0,0,,Sedikit lagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.73,0:19:28.41,Utama,Mie,0,0,0,,Aku juga bisa melihat jelas dengan kacamata baruku.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.02,0:19:32.01,Miring,Mie,0,0,0,,Rasanya kesenanganku dua kali lipat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.10,0:19:33.82,Miring,Mie,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.23,0:19:40.18,Miring,Mie,0,0,0,,Rasa-rasanya aku selalu membayangkan Komura-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.99,0:19:44.39,Miring,Mie,0,0,0,,Palingan cuma perasaanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.45,0:19:46.54,Utama,Komura,0,0,0,,Panas!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.99,0:19:48.08,Utama,Komura,0,0,0,,Pe-Perih!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.47,0:19:53.08,Utama,Komura,0,0,0,,Pipi, paha, dan telinga yang\N berulang kali aku cubit jadi terasa perih!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.09,0:20:04.09,Class,Text,0,0,0,,{\pos(433.672,110.667)}Kelas 2-B
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.10,0:20:12.60,Miring,Komura,0,0,0,,Dia Mie-san, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.81,0:20:14.90,Utama,Komura,0,0,0,,A-Ada apa, Mie-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.90,0:20:15.90,Utama,Komura,0,0,0,,Kamu baik-baik saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.90,0:20:16.75,Utama,Komura,0,0,0,,Kau demam?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.17,0:20:18.21,Utama,Mie,0,0,0,,Iya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.21,0:20:19.68,Utama,Mie,0,0,0,,Mungkin gejala demam.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.68,0:20:22.83,Utama,Mie,0,0,0,,Tapi enggak masalah, jadi tenang saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.58,0:20:27.70,Miring,Komura,0,0,0,,Nafasnya membuat kacamatanya penuh embun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.33,0:20:32.71,Miring,Komura,0,0,0,,Yah, bagaimanapun kondisinya, Mie-san tetaplah imut.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.12,0:20:34.90,Utama,Mie,0,0,0,,Susah lihat, deh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.90,0:20:36.33,Utama,Male Student,0,0,0,,Komura, sini bentar.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.92,0:20:39.06,Utama,Komura,0,0,0,,Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.98,0:20:46.04,Utama,Male Student 2,0,0,0,,Apaan coba, Tokita?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.04,0:20:48.52,Utama,Male Student 3,0,0,0,,Kacamatamu berembun, kayak orang aneh!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.52,0:20:49.97,Utama,Tokita,0,0,0,,Berisik!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.48,0:20:51.52,Utama,Tokita,0,0,0,,Apa boleh buat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.52,0:20:52.76,Utama,Male Student 2,0,0,0,,Maaf, maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.76,0:20:53.98,Utama,Male Student 2,0,0,0,,Apa kau demam?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.31,0:20:57.17,Utama,Male Student 3,0,0,0,,Yah, tapi lucu banget, sih.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.17,0:20:58.99,Utama,Tokita,0,0,0,,Berisik!{\i1}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.74,0:21:04.37,Utama,Mob Male A,0,0,0,,Kemudian membalik keadaan dan menang.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.69,0:21:09.64,Miring,Komura,0,0,0,,"Orang aneh! Lucunya!"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.06,0:21:21.28,Utama,Komura,0,0,0,,Mi-Mie-san, mana kacamatamu?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.28,0:21:22.96,Utama,Mie,0,0,0,,A-Aku lupa.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.96,0:21:24.76,Utama,Komura,0,0,0,,Eh? Tapi barusan ....
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.00,0:21:26.52,Utama,Mie,0,0,0,,Aku lupa!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.52,0:21:27.43,Utama,Komura,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.44,0:21:38.94,Utama,Komura,0,0,0,,Kenapa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.30,0:23:13.28,Utama,Komura,0,0,0,,Aku Komura Kaede.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.57,0:23:15.12,Utama,Komura,0,0,0,,Aku akan memberi cuplikan episode berikutnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.53,0:23:17.50,Utama,Komura,0,0,0,,Kali ini harus kulakukan dengan benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.50,0:23:20.75,Utama,Komura,0,0,0,,Karena ini adalah cuplikan penting anime Mie-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.63,0:23:24.80,Utama,Komura,0,0,0,,Suatu hari, Mie-san mengambil surat cinta--
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.80,0:23:25.88,Utama,Komura,0,0,0,,Mie-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.88,0:23:27.96,Utama,Komura,0,0,0,,Kenapa kau ambil, sih?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.96,0:23:29.70,Utama,Komura,0,0,0,,Apa kau lupa kacamata lagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.70,0:23:32.14,Utama,Komura,0,0,0,,Surat cinta dari siapa, sih?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.78,0:23:36.47,Utama,Komura,0,0,0,,Se-Selanjutnya, "Gadis Taksiranku Ngambil Surat Cinta."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.75,0:23:38.27,Utama,Komura,0,0,0,,Tungguin saja!
